title: Narendra Modi greets Manmohan Singh on his birthday
text:
Other Articles Meizu Pro 5 flagship smartphone launched in China, features Exynos 7420 processor, 3GB RAM Swamy's remark about JNU students shows frustration, says AAP Political wave in Bihar will turn into tsunami after PM Modi's arrival, says BJP Prime Minister Narendra Modi today greeted his predecessor Manmohan Singh on his birthday.
“I wish Dr. Manmohan Singh on his birthday and pray to Almighty that he remains in good health and leads a long life,” the Prime Minister said.
Born on September 26, 1932 in Gah, which is now in the Pakistani side of Punjab, Singh was the Prime Minister of India from 2004 to 2014.
 26, 2015 11:02 am
